					<description><![CDATA[<p><img width="600" height="900" src="https://firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/image-99.png" class="attachment-post-thumbnail size-post-thumbnail wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/image-99.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/image-99.png?resize=97%2C146&amp;ssl=1 97w" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px" /></p>
