<figure class="aligncenter size-full is-resized"><img decoding="async" width="600" height="467" src="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/image-84.png?resize=600%2C467&#038;ssl=1" alt="" class="wp-image-238574" style="width:716px;height:auto" srcset="https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/image-84.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/firenews.com.tw/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/image-84.png?resize=188%2C146&amp;ssl=1 188w" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px" data-recalc-dims="1" /><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">家貓長期與人類共存，逐漸演化出擅長對視與傳遞情感的能力，這有助於爭取食物與庇護。圖:unsplash</figcaption></figure></div>


<p>雖然貓咪的眼神足以讓人心軟，但牠們更希望看到的是人類的回應，當貓咪緩慢眨眼時，不妨以相同方式回應，這不僅能讓牠感到安心，也能增強彼此之間的情感紐帶 !</p>
